What is Laser Chess?
--------------------
Laser chess: http://www.laserchess.org/

Our objective is to design and implement a parallel laser chess
program.

How to use?
-----------
Compile with
 
$  g++ -o lchess piece.cpp board.cpp lchess.cpp move.cpp

Run as

$ ./lchess

Input Format
-----------

Move: 'M <src X coord 0-8> <src Y coord 0-8> <dst X> <dst Y>' e.g 'M 1 0 2 0'

Rotate: 'R <src X> <src Y> <angle 90/-90 >' e.g. 'R 1 0 -90'

